## MONERO WORKFLOW
Offline:
    [cold_sign_tx.sh] —> .txn file
        ↓
    [encrypt_tx.py]   —> .txn.gpg
        ↓ [USB]
Online:
    [decrypt_tx.py]   —> .txn
        ↓
    [hot_broadcast_tx.sh] —> Network

ASCII Diagram:
 [ COLD WALLET ] --> .txn --> GPG --> USB --> [ HOT WALLET ]
                                        ↓
                               decrypt_tx.py → monero-wallet-rpc

